Real GPS constellation TLE fixture
==================================

gps-ops_2021-07-28.txt
  A genuine Celestrak `gps-ops` two-line-element snapshot of the operational GPS
  constellation, catalogued 2021-07-28 (epoch day 209 of 2021), 30 satellites.
  Two-line element sets are open data: they originate from the US Space Force /
  18th Space Defense Squadron catalogue and are redistributed by Celestrak
  (Dr T. S. Kelso). This file is used by tests/igs_real_data.rs to validate the
  real-TLE -> SGP4 -> Earth-fixed geometry path against a real constellation,
  rather than only synthetic Walker patterns.

This file is not part of the Kshana source and is not shipped in the published
crates/packages (see the `exclude` list in Cargo.toml); it exists only for the
test suite.
